Package: slicer
Title: Sliced Wasserstein Distances for Regression
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jan", "Vanhove", , "janvanhove@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4607-4836"))
Description: Wasserstein and sliced Wasserstein distances between empirical 
    distributions as well as kernels derived from them. 
    Includes functions for fitting Gaussian process regression using 
    these kernels.
URL: https://github.com/janhove/slicer, https://janhove.github.io/slicer/
